    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>An article in Business Day yesterday about the turnaround effort at the Ford Motor Company misstated the number and timing of plant closings under its restructuring plan. Ford will close 16 plants, not 14. And nine of those plants, not all 16, will close by 2008. The rest will close by 2012.</p>
      </block>
